Coming this Fall... available for 4-5 months, possibly longer. Perfect for incoming Congressional reps/staff while you get your bearings in DC. Showings begin November 1st. <br>
Rosslyn, with garage parking/balcony/pool/gym. Furnished rental for one person:<br>
Large sunny corner unit, 1br/ 1 bath. Fully FURNISHED rental, available after the November midterms. Ideal for incoming Congressional reps/staff while you house hunt and get your bearings in DC. 2 blocks to Rosslyn Metro. 3 stops from Pentagon. Seeking a quiet, responsible tenant. Just bring clothes/toiletries. Everything else provided including sheets, towels, pots and pans, coffee maker, toaster oven, etc. ALL utilities included plus Wifi! There is a Smart TV with air antenna for local channels, Roku device for steaming. Great building, staffed gate and front desk, fitness center/gym, mail room, laundry room on same floor as unit. Balcony with distant monument views and ONE medium size garage parking space, very convenient. NO pets or smokers. Great neighborhood, easy 1 mile walk over Key Bridge to Georgetown/DC. Easy bike ride to Pentagon, Mall, Old Town. You will have one large bedroom closet, linen closet and another for storage plus a vanity + cabinet in the bathroom for toiletries. Onsite barber and market! Target and Safeway are walking distance, plus so many restaurants, new Gold's gym, etc. Your $50 app fee will register you with the building HOA and allow you package/lockout service and access to the GYM/pool! Call  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/wdc/apa/7509106882/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
 for info. First, last and damage due at lease signing: $6,900. Then just pay rent on the first for additional months. Professional reference and (free) credit report required. $100/month military discount with ID.  ** NO Smokers/NO Pets/NO co-signers.
